<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="h-full">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error-Laundry Manager</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="h-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
        <div class="mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-24 w-24 text-blue-500 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">¡Ups! Algo salió mal</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Parece que nuestras máquinas de lavado están un poco confundidas. No te preocupes, ¡pronto tendremos todo limpio y ordenado!</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <button onclick="window.history.back()" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 w-full">
                Volver a la página anterior
            </button>
            <a href="/login" class="inline-block bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-800 font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 w-full">
                Ir al inicio de sesión
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Animación simple para el icono de la lavadora
        const washingMachine = document.querySelector('svg');
        let rotation = 0;
        setInterval(() => {
            rotation += 5;
            washingMachine.style.transform = `rotate(${rotation}deg)`;
        }, 50);
    </script>
</body>
</html>